title: MATLAB Graphics and Data Visualization Cookbook
description:
MATLAB Graphics and Data Visualization Cookbook (Packt Publishing, 2012).pdf

ISBN 978-1-84969-316-5

Written for undergraduate and graduate students, MATLAB Graphics and Data Visualization Cookbook provides a collection of data visualization recipes with functionalized versions of common tasks for easy integration into your data analysis workflow. The recipes are cross-referenced with MATLAB product pages and MATLAB Central File Exchange resources for improved coverage. Topics include one, two, three and high dimensional plots, volumetric data presentation, and customizing elements of MATLAB graphics
